# Netlify redirects and rewrites

# SPA fallback - serve index.html for all routes
/*    /index.html   200

# API redirects (if needed)
/api/*  https://api.omnix-ai.com/:splat  200

# Security redirects
/wp-admin/*  https://example.com  301
/wordpress/*  https://example.com  301
/wp-content/*  https://example.com  301

# Force HTTPS (if not handled by hosting)
http://omnix-ai.com/*  https://omnix-ai.com/:splat  301!
http://www.omnix-ai.com/*  https://omnix-ai.com/:splat  301!

# Canonical redirects
https://www.omnix-ai.com/*  https://omnix-ai.com/:splat  301!